<p>Back at it again with another <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hf2esGA7vCc&amp;list=PLjEaoINr3zgEL9UjPTLWQhLFAK7wVaRMR" class="link">BenderGuru tutorial series</a> - but this time, a chair. The tutorial used a set of refence photos of an existing chair, with the goal of creating a 3d model as close to the original as possible. 
<br /></p>
